<!-- Areas of Focus Section -->
<section id="focus" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Areas of Focus</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Policy Research & Recommendations</h3>
        <p>Conducting evidence-based research to shape policies that address complex, interconnected social issues, with solutions that work in both national and when needed, global contexts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Human Rights</h3>
        <p>Advancing equity by focusing on the upliftment of communities facing systemic barriers, ensuring freedom from discrimination and building pathways to dignity for all.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Women</h3>
        <p>Driving both grassroots initiatives and policy measures that strengthen women's rights, amplify their voices, and expand their representation in decision-making spaces.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Health Access</h3>
        <p>Improving primary and localised healthcare systems to deliver consistent, high-quality services, ensuring that essential care is accessible to every community.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-primary-600">Practical Education</h3>
        <p>Filling the gap left by traditional schooling by equipping all age groups with essential real-world knowledge, from financial literacy to legal awareness.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
